{"tid":1901741,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"喂成班港豬，係咪已經唔記得咗陳茂波係咩人？","createTime":"2020-02-28T03:57:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T04:10:36.000Z","uid":301388,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a284cfb6eb15507e04fae1a8f926074659940644","tid":1901741,"uid":301388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T03:57:24.000Z","msg":"1. 囤地 - 【硬銷東北 陳茂波囤地自肥】<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20130722/18343730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20130722%2F18343730&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0VKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=5d0cb208\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20130722%2F18343730&h=a11ec0a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20130722/18343730</a><br />\n2. 誹謗 - 【法庭：漢基校董告陳茂波誹謗】<br />\n<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20120309/00176_069.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20120309%2F00176_069.html&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0VKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=6ad18802\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20120309/00176_069.html</a><br />\n3. 醉駕 - 【海難港人傷痛時 陳茂波隊啤醉駕】<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.dv.nextmedia.com/actionnews/hit/20121004/18031887/20002333\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.dv.nextmedia.com%2Factionnews%2Fhit%2F20121004%2F18031887%2F20002333&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0VKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=97993055\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.dv.nextmedia.com%2Factionnews%2Fhit%2F20121004%2F18031887%2F20002333&h=3e1bc16e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.dv.nextmedia.com/actionnews/hit/20121004/18031887/20002333</a><br />\n4. 劏房 - 【劏房局長放生僭建特首】<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20120731/16561946\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20120731%2F16561946&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0VKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=dd95e5f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20120731%2F16561946&h=78cbda2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20120731/16561946</a><br />\n<br />\n跟住再睇下佢究竟係點撚樣上位嘅，原來次次都係執雞：<br />\n2012年，時任發展局局長麥齊光因爲涉嫌騙取政府房屋津貼下台，陳茂波接替麥齊光出任發展局局長。<br />\n2016年，時任財政司司長曾俊華辭職參選特首，陳茂波接替曾俊華出任財政司司長。<br />\n2020年，佢諗住派下錢就可以搏中共炒林鄭之後頂上做特首，然之後成班港豬個個心諗錢已袋理撚得你，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>對唔對得住為咗香港連命都唔要嘅手足？</strong></span></span></span>"},{"pid":"2cca683d3dbc2737a14a2cc94f3c9237334000eb","tid":1901741,"uid":146737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T03:58:04.000Z","msg":"【第貳拾柒期牆紙】 工會抗暴政<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1897739/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1897739/page/1</a><br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0VKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=c036a07e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a><br />\nFB : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/852wallpaper/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F852wallpaper%2F&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0VKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=0444a301\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/852wallpaper/</a><br />\nIG : <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hongkong_wallpaper/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fhongkong_wallpaper%2F&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0VKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=c712b547\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/hongkong_wallpaper/</a><br />\nWEB: <a href=\"https://firsthand-news.web.app/wallpaper/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https